      "writtenOn": "2021-02-18T10:11:51Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I\u0027m not sure if it is better to have this an optional attribute like wificell_unstable. I think the test \"suites\" other than wificell_func probably won\u0027t separate the suspend/resume case so I think this is simpler to have this as another \"suite\" instead of a \"property\".\n\n@Dean, WDYT?",
