      "writtenOn": "2021-02-19T05:23:07Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Make it an optional attribute is fine. However, it should be named \"wificell_suspend\".\n\nAnother thing comes in my mind is that we have \"wificell_stress\". All (or most of) the stress tests have suspend/resume action, right? I\u0027m not sure if it is a good idea to merge the two attributes.",
      "parentUuid": "c337164b_2641587d",
      "revId": "1beaf83558a1a2199a787fe84825de7b412e45ef",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba"
    },
