      "writtenOn": "2021-02-19T05:32:21Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I prefer having it as a separate suite so I\u0027ll keep it as is.\n\nFor wificell_stress reuse, I think we still want to separate the two, because we probably don\u0027t want to run stress tests (which usually takes hours) in wifi_matfunc/AVL.",
